node.text:
Struggling with writer's block, a novelist finds inspiration when she meets a down-on-his-luck oddball who constantly changes personas and alter egos to cope with the past and avoid reality.

With: @ilizasheslinger @davidkoechner @cleopatracoleman @trezzo_ @nickthune #ad #therightonemovie

May be a Twitter screenshot of one or more people and text that says 'eiri @EirianeddMunro Depression presents itself in subtle forms: messy room, dirty clothes, unwashed dishes, laying in bed 24/7, not showering, skipping meals, cancelling plans Its hard to spot, its harder to talk about but its impossible to get them back once theyre gone. Dont ignore the signs. Ask. Georgie brown #letsgo @Georgie66291217 A few weeks ago walked into my brothers room and moaned at the state of it he told me he was depressed said it was an excuse 3 days ago they pulled his body out the river, if someone talks LISTEN'.
